channel.title: Is it just me?
channel.description:
Well, this has nothing to do with me what so ever, it's mainly about my friend.
Well, my friend I think is extremely jealous of everyone, and all of us are starting to get a little bit sick of it. He's quick to use other peoples stuff and rely on other people to buy his lunch because he doesn't want his healthy lunch, he'd rather eat chicken burgers and stuff, typical fat attitude (I don't want to call him fat but theres no other words for it, he's pretty obese). Today I bought him a ice-block and at lunch I asked if he had 10 cents because I was a little short. He told me to fuck off and get my own money and I was a little pissed about that.
Well, it's always been like that, but lately it's gotten worse. He's saying things behind peoples backs, causing conflict etc. Now the problem has escelated into the internet. All my friends I have met from moparisthebest he wants to know. A perfect example is haxed who is one of my best e-friends. I play with him on CoD4 quite a lot. Now my friend has gone and met him and just decided he's his best friend and is going to join our clan etc. and begins saying I said he's a fag and stuff. Luckily haxed knows I wouldn't and told me and stuff.
I really don't know what to do, normally people get flamed in this situation but I have really no one else to talk to because he's been my friend since kindergarten. (The one where you like 5 years, first year of school)
